high_descs: Turn left and move to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter to the left of the sink.
Take a step to the right to stand in front of the right sink.
Slice the lettuce in the right sink with the knife.
Take a step to the left to stand in front of the left sink and then turn right to face the dishwasher.
Open the cupboard to the right of the dishwasher and place the knife inside.
Turn back around to face the sink.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the sink.
Turn around and carry the lettuce to the fridge.
Place the lettuce on the plate in the fridge, close the door, then open the door and remove the lettuce after a couple seconds.
Turn around and move to the green trash bin in the corner across from the fridge.
Place the slice of lettuce in the green trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a slice of cold lettuce.

high_descs: Turn left and move to the sink in front of the window.
Pick up the knife between the loaf of bread and the sink from the counter.
Move to the right and face the sink.
Slice the head of lettuce in the sink using the knife.
Turn to the right and face the dishwasher underneath the microwave.
Open the cabinet door to the right of the dishwasher, place the knife on top of the ladle, then close the cabinet door.
Turn to the left and face the sink.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the sink.
Turn around and move to the silver refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator, place the lettuce on the plate on the bottom shelf, let the lettuce chill in the refrigerator, then open the refrigerator, pick up the slice of lettuce, and then close the refrigerator door.
Turn around and move to the green rubbish bin to the left of the range.
Place the slice of lettuce in the rubbish bin to the left of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of lettuce in the rubbish bin.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the sink
Pick up the knife that is to the right of the loaf of bread on the counter
Turn right and then turn left and go to the larger of the two sinks
Slice the head of lettuce in half that is in the larger sink
Turn left then turn right to face the smaller sink, then turn right
Open the cupboard to the right of the dishwasher and put the knife inside
Turn left to face the two sinks
Cut a slice of the lettuce that is in the larger sink and pick up the slice
Turn around and go to the wall then turn left to face the fridge
Put the slice of lettuce in the fridge to chill then take it back out
Turn around and head to the green garbage bin that is between the stove and the wall
Put the slice of lettuce in the green garbage bin
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of chilled lettuce in a garbage bin
